He emphasized that General Secretary Xi Jinping’s important thoughts on strengthening and improving the work of the CPPCC profoundly clarified the status, role, goals and tasks, responsibilities and missions of the CPPCC, and practical requirements, and scientifically answered a series of major directional, overall, and strategic issues. , is a powerful ideological weapon to guide the work of the CPPCC in the new era.
