This move will restore U.S. sanctions lifted under the 2015 Iran nuclear deal and add 300 new sanctions on Iran&#39;s oil, shipping, insurance and banking industries.
Details of the sanctions will be announced by Secretary of State Mike Pompeo and Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin at a press conference at 1330 GMT.
