Recently, the General Office of the Ministry of Education issued the &quot;Notice on the Progress of the Rectification Work of the National Special Governance Action for Off-campus Training Institutions&quot;. As of October 15, 2018, a total of 400,532 off-campus training institutions nationwide have been identified, and 272,175 institutions with problems have been completed. 83,510 institutions were rectified, with a rectification rate of 30.68%.
