On June 26, 2018, a woman from Anshan City, Liaoning Province went missing, and her family called the local police.
After investigation and judgment by the police, this was not a simple case of missing persons. The missing person Bai was most likely killed by his lover Wang. The police immediately set up a task force to conduct further investigation.
On October 30, the task force discovered that the criminal suspect Wang might be hiding in Dongsheng District, Ordos City. The Dongsheng police immediately organized a capable police force to fully cooperate with the Liaoning police in detecting the case.
After five days of investigation, the police finally found out Wang’s whereabouts and conducted a detailed combing of his related persons.
On November 4, police from the two places worked together to capture the suspect Wang in an excavator parts store in Dongsheng District.
According to Wang&#39;s account, he and the victim Bai were lovers. Because Bai&#39;s sister had a large sum of money temporarily deposited in Bai&#39;s name, the two decided to take the money as their own.
On June 22, 2018, Wang and Bai had a disagreement over the use of the funds. Wang then killed Bai in a rental house, decomposed the body and dumped it.
At present, the criminal suspect Wang has been handed over to the police in Anshan, Liaoning.
